reviewText: Most of the dvd is Kenny and crew talking and getting ready for the tour.  Not a concert type of dvd.  More like a documentary about the concert.

DO NOT pay 42 dollars for a USED copy of this dvd! This is available at Kenny's web site BRAND NEW for 19 dollars! Not very rare at all.
That being said, this is better than the 1st Road Case dvd. If you're a fan, and liked the 1st Road Case, get this, but get it from KC's web site.
